summary: real looking preset based on NLA v1.4
descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][center][b][i]What is Real Nature ENB ?[/i][/b]

Real Nature ENB is a realistic ENB config using latest ENB version. This preset is based on awesome NLA 1.4
[youtube]cFWjofLOYXU[/youtube]
[img]http://static-1.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/60374-2-1417278183.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static-4.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/60374-1-1417278318.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/60374-3-1417278385.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/60374-4-1417278319.jpg[/img]
[b]WHAT YOU NEED

[u]Latest ENB files: [/u][url=http://enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.html]http://enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.html[/url]
[u]The helper plugin: [/u][url=http://www.dev-c.com/skyrim/enbhelper/]http://www.dev-c.com/skyrim/enbhelper/[/url]

For ENBSeries to work properly the following values must be set to 1 in SkyrimPrefs.ini:
bFloatPointRenderTarget=1
bTreesReceiveShadows=1
bDrawLandShadows=1
bShadowsOnGrass=1


[/b][b]Recomended mods
